Width (ft): Weighted avg bankfull width from OCGIS web tool Lidar profile
Depth (ft): Weighted avg bankfull depth from OCGIS web tool Lidar profiles
R1: Weighted avg bottom width coefficient from OCGIS profiles
R2: Weighted avg floodplain slope from OCGIS web tool Lidar profile
W1: Weighted avg floodplain width coefficient from OCGIS profiles
Mannings n: Weighted avg n from channels shp and Mannings Crosswalk
